Phumelela Gaming of South Africa First-Half Profit Falls as Revenue Drops

-- B y   P a u l   R i c h a r d s o n
-- 
2011-04-08T05:11:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-08/phumelela-gaming-of-south-africa-first-half-profit-falls-as-revenue-drops.html
Phumelela Gaming and Leisure Ltd., a
South African organizer of horse races and betting, said first-
half profit fell 15 percent to 34.9 million rand ($5.25
million).  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  